        "code": "def _shared_mod_inverse(base, mod):\n    \"\"\"Compute modular inverse of base modulo mod using fast exponentiation.\"\"\"\n    exp = mod - 2\n    res = 1\n    while exp:\n        if exp & 1:\n            res = (res * base) % mod\n        base = (base * base) % mod\n        exp >>= 1\n    return res"
